OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782362901
OL,3,CForecasters warn of even higher
OL,4,Ctemperatures amid sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FThe heatwave brought record-breaking
OL,7,Ftemperatures on Wednesday, with
OL,8,Fforecasters warning they could rise
OL,9,Feven higher.
OL,11,FA rare red warning for extreme heat
OL,12,Fhas been issued by the Met Office as
OL,13,Fthe UK has sweltered in exceptionally
OL,14,Fhot and humid conditions.
OL,16,FProvisional figures suggest the
OL,17,Ftemperature reached 36.1C in Gosport,
OL,18,FHampshire, breaking the previous June
OL,19,Frecord from the summer of 1976.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
