CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782362901
OL,3,CForecasters warn of even higher
OL,4,Ctemperatures amid sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FHowever some places might feel
OL,7,Fslightly cooler due to a brisk breeze
OL,8,Fin the south, it said.
OL,10,FRed warnings for extreme heat have
OL,11,Fbeen issued for an area from London
OL,12,Fand the south coast to Swansea,
OL,13,FSomerset and Birmingham until late on
OL,14,FThursday.
OL,16,FThe forecaster warned that
OL,17,F"significant disruption to daily life
OL,18,Fis likely".
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@JO]
