OL,3,CForecasters warn of even higher
OL,4,Ctemperatures amid sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FIf temperatures reach 39C, that would
OL,7,Fmake it the second hottest day in the
OL,8,FUK on record.
OL,10,FIf 38C is recorded, that is still in
OL,11,Fthe top five days ever recorded and
OL,12,Fhotter than any day of the 20th
OL,13,Fcentury.
OL,15,FThe heatwave has led to health
OL,16,Fwarnings, school closures and
OL,17,Ftransport disruption.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
