OL,3,CForecasters warn of even higher
OL,4,Ctemperatures amid sweltering heatwave
OL,6,FIt is driven by a "heat-dome" settling
OL,7,Fover western Europe that has brought
OL,8,Fextreme conditions across the
OL,9,Fcontinent.
OL,11,FRed heat health alerts have also been
OL,12,Fissued by the UK Health Security
OL,13,FAgency (UKHSA) for the East of
OL,14,FEngland, East Midlands, London, the
OL,15,FSouth East, the South West and the
OL,16,FWest Midlands, and amber heat health
OL,17,Falerts for the North East, North West,
OL,18,Fand Yorkshire and The Humber.
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@]O]
